items.title: Market Today: State elections, Israel War, Oil, Garuda Construction IPO
items.description: At 6:38 AM, GIFT Nifty Futures were trading 114 points lower at 24,871, indicating a potential gap-down opening for Indian markets.

items.title: 3 startups look to raise $400 mn as US biotech IPOs gain traction
items.description: September was the busiest month for healthcare IPOs this year, Dealogic data showed. Strong debuts by companies such as BioAge Labs and Bicara Therapeutics have also encouraged listings

items.title: Garuda Construction IPO opens: GMP rises marginally; should you subscribe?
items.description: Garuda Construction has succeeded in garnering reviews from several brokerages including Anand Rathi Research, SMIFS, and Arihant Capital Markets for its IPO

items.title: Sebi greenlights NSDL IPO: NSE, HDFC Bank, among others to pare stakes
items.description: The Sebi nod for the NSDL IPO came more than a year after the company submitted its DRHP to Sebi on July 7, 2023

items.title: Zinka Logistics gets Sebi nod for Rs 550-cr IPO; key details for investors
items.description: Through the IPO, Zinka Logistics is offering a fresh issue of shares of up to Rs 550 crore and an offer for sale of up to 21.61 million equity shares, with a face value of Re 1 apiece
